Kyushu.title: Kyushu
Kyushu.byline: Kyūshū (Japanese: 九州) is the southernmost of the four main islands of Japan.

Kyustendil.title: Kyustendil
Kyustendil.byline: Kyustendil (Bulgarian: Кюстендил) is a city in Central Western Bulgaria, under the slopes of the Osogovo Mountain which straddles the border with North Macedonia.
